        <item>
            <title>【评测】Sennheiser ACCENTUM Wireless 真无线蓝牙头戴式耳机　外观型格+音色靓+性价比高</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/20/sennheiser-accentum-wireless/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=sennheiser-accentum-wireless</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/20/sennheiser-accentum-wireless/mobile-music/headphones/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 10:16:13 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[音乐耳机]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[ACCENTUM Wireless]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Sennheiser]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Sennheiser ACCENTUM Wireless]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1205124</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Sennheiser 继上年推出的 MOMENTUM 4 Wireless 后，再次推出新款无线蓝牙头戴式耳机 ACCENTUM Wireless。小编用后就觉得承传了 Sennheiser 舒服的音色，价钱方面属中价位，但表现似乎不差过旗舰耳机，整体性价比都几高。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1205322 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00029-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00029-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00029-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00029-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00029-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00029-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Sennheiser ACCENTUM Wireless</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>黑白两色，低调设计不易留痕</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">ACCENTUM Wireless 的设计及外观颇为简洁直观，整个耳机只有侧面印有细小的 Sennheiser 标示，小编颇喜欢低调的设计。机身用上了磨砂质地，不易留下指纹等污渍。机底有个 USB-C 充电位。ACCENTUM Wireless 有 2 款颜色选择，小编拿到的是黑色，型格之选。另外还有白色，感觉优雅高贵，比较会适合女士。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1205326 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00032-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00032-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00032-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00032-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00032-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00032-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲整个耳机只有侧面印有细小的 Sennheiser 标示，小编颇喜欢低调的设计</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1205334 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00031-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00031-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00031-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00031-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00031-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00031-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲机身用上了磨砂质地，不易留下指纹等污渍</p><h2><strong>耳罩不焗促 </strong><strong>佩戴感舒适</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">ACCENTUM Wireless 包装简单，省却了收纳袋和盒，随机会附送  1 条 USB-C 充电线。ACCENTUM Wireless 是头罩式耳机，有一定份量，机身只重 22.2 克，小编戴了 3 小时未感不适，耳罩用料记忆绵，不感焗促外，亦舒服稳阵，不会轻易掉下。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1205328 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00036-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00036-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00036-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00036-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00036-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00036-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲耳罩用料记忆绵，不感焗促外，亦舒服稳阵</p><h2><strong>保留实体键，感觉实在</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">ACCENTUM Wireless 使用了实体键，而非旗舰耳机的轻触式设计，小编反而觉得几好，一方面操控相对直接容易，按下更有实感，另一方面可确保不会误触。操控方面颇为简单，最底在 USB-C 充电口旁的按键是开关掣，长按 3 秒可开关，5 秒则可连接蓝牙，连接速度快。对上 3 粒按键，由上而下分别是大声，暂停或播放音乐及细声。惟一要投诉的，是欠缺了切换主动降噪和通透模式按键。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1205330 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00041-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00041-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00041-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00041-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00041-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00041-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲实体键操控相对直接容易，按下更有实感</p><h2><strong>Sennheiser Smart Control </strong><strong>自定义 </strong><strong>EQ</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">Sennheiser 向来都有自家应用程式，用家可以下载 Smart Control，调整主动降噪、通透模式、EQ 等。主动降噪可选择开启或关闭减少风声。EQ 方面就预设 2 项，分别是 Bass Boost 及 Podcast，假如用家对 EQ 未有太多认识，或许未能满足需求。Sennheiser 似乎鼓励用家自行调节。用家亦可自定通话时，聆听多少自己的声音。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1205371 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2520-2-313x580.jpg" alt="" width="313" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2520-2-313x580.jpg 313w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2520-2-485x900.jpg 485w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2520-2-768x1425.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2520-2.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 313px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1205372 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2523-694x492.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="492" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2523-694x492.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2523-768x544.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2523.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可切换 ANC 及通透模式</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1205373 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2522-309x580.jpg" alt="" width="309" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2522-309x580.jpg 309w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2522-480x900.jpg 480w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2522-768x1440.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2522-819x1536.jpg 819w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2522.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 309px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可调 EQ</p><h2><strong>多装置连接</strong></h2><p>Sennheiser ACCENTUM Wireless 有多装置连接，用家可同时连上电脑及手机，小编工作时经常不止用一个装置，所以觉得这功能非常实用。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1205370 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2521-2-292x580.jpg" alt="" width="292" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2521-2-292x580.jpg 292w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2521-2-453x900.jpg 453w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2521-2-768x1527.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2521-2-773x1536.jpg 773w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2521-2.jpg 805w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 292px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Sennheiser ACCENTUM Wireless 有多装置连接</p><h2><strong>支援快速充电，充电</strong><strong> 10 分钟可用 5 小时</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">续航力方面，充满电的 ACCENTUM Wireless 可以连续使用 50 小时，起长的使用时间足够小编长时使用 4 至 5 日。ACCENTUM Wireless 支援快速充电，只要充电 10 分钟，即可使用 5 小时，可谓是惊人。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1205329 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00033-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00033-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00033-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00033-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00033-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00033-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲充满电的 ACCENTUM Wireless 可以连续使用 50 小时，快速充电，只要充电 10 分钟，即可使用 5 小时</p><h2><strong>通话表现良好</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">由于可在 Sennheiser Smart Control 内调整聆听多少自己的声音，加上有 Hybrid ANC，因此 ACCENTUM Wireless 通话表现良好，如果在室内通话绝对没问题，室外可能会有少许风噪声。Jabra Elite 5 使用，了 SBC、AAC 以及 aptX，全都是基本配置，在 Android 手机上收听理论上会好一点，但音乐来源亦会影响音色。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1205331 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00039-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00039-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00039-1-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00039-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00039-1-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/DSC00039-1-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Hybrid ANC 室内通话绝对没问题</p><h2><strong>人声</strong><strong>低频</strong><strong>柔和 </strong><strong>三频平衡好</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">小编在 iPhone 上使用 Moov 播放邓丽欣的《他不准我哭》，人声靠近突出，音色甜美。再试试陈奕迅的《富士山下》，不止人声出色，音乐的分析力就不俗，清楚听到配乐组合，低音结他和鼓声不会突兀，很柔和，力度份量刚好。喜欢重低音的用家可自行设置 EQ，令低频更突出。小编认为 ACCENTUM Wireless 适合听流行歌，未必适合听多配乐，多层次的摇滚音乐。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1205336 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2511-313x580.jpg" alt="" width="313" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2511-313x580.jpg 313w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2511-485x900.jpg 485w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2511-768x1425.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2511.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 313px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲邓丽欣《他不准我哭》</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1205337 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2516-313x580.jpg" alt="" width="313" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2516-313x580.jpg 313w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2516-485x900.jpg 485w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2516-768x1425.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/IMG_2516.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 313px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲陈奕迅《富士山下》</p><h2><strong>总结：音色出众 </strong><strong>电量够</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">ACCENTUM Wireless 的售价为 HK$ 1499，属中价位，但做到高水准，的确有 Sennheiser 的高级感和音色，再加上续航力达 50 小时。如此的规格，性价比极高，适合有要求，长时间使用者。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>

